arning from Human Feedback</td><td>9</td></tr>\n        <tr><td>RNN</td><td>Recurrent Neural Network</td><td>3</td></tr>\n        <tr><td>SGD</td><td>Stochastic Gradient Descent</td><td>2</td></tr>\n        <tr><td>VAE</td><td>Variational Autoencoder</td><td>6</td></tr>\n        <tr><td>VLM</td><td>Vision-Language Model</td><td>10</td></tr>\n        <tr><td>VQA</td><td>Visual Question Answering</td><td>10</td></tr>\n      </tbody>\n    </table>\n\n    <div class=\"callout info\">\n      <div class=\"callout-title\">ðŸ’¡ Using This Glossary</div>\n      <p>This glossary provides quick definitions. For comprehensive coverage of any topic, refer to the chapter indicated in italics.</p>\n    </div>

